item.description:
An Tua Nua is a great venue, not too far from the Fenway/Kenmore area, which has karaoke on wednesday nights! It's a nice bar with good food, and they have salsa wednesday nights in the neighboring room so there's something for everyone! ***note, there's no cover for the karaoke, but I think there is a cover for the salsa...***

Hope to see you there, whether you're singing or cheering on the singers!
item.how_to_find_us: must sign up for the meetup to find out!
